{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41b314fc3b","title":"周恩来戚本禹接见广西双方代表的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7c6a8cdb23","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"41b314fc3b"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"440b5f1bc1","name":"黄永胜","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"6c3c62f283","name":"罗瑞卿","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9da523fb00","name":"广西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"},{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bdae07d0d5","type":"title","text":"周恩来戚本禹接见广西双方代表的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3c75ed366e","type":"authors","text":"周恩来戚本禹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3080e08cb4","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：一九六七年八月二十四日凌晨一点十分至四点四十五分，地点：人民大会堂小礼堂。出席者：广西4·22，广西联指，广西军区，柳州军分区，6955部队和55军代表，广西区党委书记处书记伍晋南，乔晓光，安平生，霍泛，贺希明五人，广州军区司令员黄永胜在场。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"db9013558a","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理进场时，全场高呼：毛主席万岁！）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"76dbb59f72","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：很久不见你们了，两个月了，最近很忙。（很生气地）你们“联指”怎么越搞越不象话，又去进攻人家，越走越远了。你们再这样下去，我们就要全部武装他们（4·22），看你们怎么办？！4·22的同志，文革给你们的电话知道了吗？（要上交援越抗美军事物资问题）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7ee8fb769f","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：知道了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"428c908f56","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们比较听话，办得比较快。还有一部分没有收回是不是？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"10c8b76107","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：是。（接着汇报执行中央文革电话指示情况。并递上一份报告。）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"56e52192bc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们这样做不对。自卫嘛，跟军区去要。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"838604e640","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：我们是不对。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"176980d77c","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：不对！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b139b56699","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么不对？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f2637606f2","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们放在炮艇上打我们。……。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"977ca8ff10","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们（联指）方向错了，你们进攻人家（4·22），现在只剩下几个点了。你们想消灭他们，这怎么消灭得了？这怎么行！人家不服，桂林老多当然要支援他们罗！你们这样干，怎么能成为越南最可靠的后方？达成协议无效么。你们这样做，让越南人看看，影响多坏呀！你们广西要成为越南可靠的后方，别人不放心！","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4290184d36","type":"paragraph","text":"联指（广西大学的教师）：（打断总理讲话）总理，我是监督小组的，刚从南宁来，我们如实反映情况。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"6ae1554fef","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（很生气）好，我只听你一刻钟，怎么个“如实”法。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1b1d8ec0d4","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：……，他们百货大楼先开枪，……。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f5eebb8956","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我问你，什么时候来的？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"759da45a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我十三号来的。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"da2c9f5c81","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：不对，八号我们就看到他了。他当面欺骗总理，把他轰出去！","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9ffc8b9b96","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（向4·22摇摇手，又问联指）你什么时候到的。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fe4703ed4e","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是十三号到的。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"70f1736a52","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么？！十三号来，十三号到？！","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"44cdd0525c","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是坐飞机来的。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"001593aaeb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：喔。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8eb566e0c8","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（接着又讲4·22进攻他们。）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"489220fe35","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们总讲这句话。我诚恳要求你们，讲以前，先想一想，这样搞武斗不符合毛泽东思想，你们要说服下面，不要搞武斗……。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1fdf8b29ee","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们和4·22的矛盾，大量的是人民内部矛盾……。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"db4f3ec3ff","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们把他们作为敌我矛盾来打！","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e046f176e1","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：不是这么回事！","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3e2e8d514c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么不是！你们都没有敌情观念。对你们的办法就是要把美帝引进来，打敌人啦，你们就不打了。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3215a0b87a","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：内战是他们挑起的。……，他们不抓革命促生产，全面罢工，都跑出来了。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4610637911","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们把人家赶出来嘛，怎么上工？","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2317020b21","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们……。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1f3db9c9b4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们还有没有希望（不打内战）？","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9cd2fae120","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们主动要求停止。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"722dcd9633","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们在哪一点地方提出？现在伍晋南不在，你还说谁操纵？你是哪里的？","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b1ca154b2f","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是“西大”的。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c016193ac0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：哦，是大学生。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2e262e048f","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：他不是学生，是“西大”教师。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e513c35f3d","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是六五年毕业的，才当两年教师，和学生差不多。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"6b6bd80d38","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你为什么受人利用，呵！还是个教师，专门领导打内战。……","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"cf663e3ef4","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：没有。我是被赶出来的。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a966b9d1ac","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是被赶出来的，那在你那个单位一定是少数派。我问你，你们联指在南宁占多少地方？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"efe6f623fb","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（汇报西大情况）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ccc6b7c9ed","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你老是讲“西大”，我问你，你代表联指还是代表“西大”？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9c78aa32cf","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是“西大”的，我代表联指。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f110584be0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我问你！联指占了多少地方？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f1a9b3341d","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们4·22占领展览馆、广西日报、百货大楼、邕江大桥……。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e81f7b6ebc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（邕江大桥）你们不是夺了吗？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"cb1b4b91e0","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：他们想从邕江大桥运农民来。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1d09ea88e8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们（对联指）承认不承认夺了？","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fb61953abb","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：……。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9dedf087ce","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在不是在你们手里吗？你们不可以把邕江大桥交给解放军吗？","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a0dce972b5","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（汇报战况）","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4c0823a6d0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们总是汇报战况，这我不感兴趣。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2ca808c7a5","type":"paragraph","text":"（联指被迫汇报占领的地方。）","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f391f86e5d","type":"appellation","text":"（总理边记、边问）","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c74fcffff3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：就这些吗？所有的机关都被你们占领了！","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fd729b8708","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们占领的地方是得到群众拥护的。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7342382e24","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们占了人家的地方，人家还拥护你们？！","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"aaa25a7d99","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（汇报4·22在工农兵饭店抢单车）","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"52a4e71c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我问你，你们有多少大卡车？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d84f690cd3","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我不知道。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"667c122392","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们自己掌握多少汽车？","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3d3019da53","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们有“汽司”，是有汽车的。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"dd9017a2d6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们能调动多少汽车？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5365978d5f","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们的汽车是用来抓革命促生产的。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8937070886","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你避开回答问题！","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"842fe8dc15","type":"paragraph","text":"联指；我们都是如实汇报情况的。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9476c29f80","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我希望你说点真的。你们有多少人？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a48f0f723d","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：十六万多。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"33a0f1b595","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：工人多少？","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"947215005b","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：绝大部分。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c6e1559882","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：具体多少？","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"642063d7fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（联指答不上）","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"90796fcc23","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：学生多少？","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b796bc9d7e","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：二万多。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"32102c2f21","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：机关干部多少？","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"74529033e6","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：有。绝大多数。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"848e14c53c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：到底有多少？","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"635b699f56","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：一万多。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d6713821c5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：总数说有十六万，分开又说不出。（稍停）郊区农民有多少？","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"76747c15e2","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：有九万多。","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5c56d84528","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这么说，一半城市的，一半农村的罗！","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ea8a8f3c99","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：农民不算在十六万里面。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"00814eded2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：农民到底有多少在你们这边？","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"90df2d4801","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：95％参加联指。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e91de06036","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：到底有多少？","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4d83b500d5","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：七万多。","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9c02200b22","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不对。九九八十一，九五四十五，八万六嘛。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bb00fea299","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：……无话可答。（全场轰笑）","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9f80af6af9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：加起来二十五万，都在你们这边。怪不得你们压人家。（稍停）你们有多少汽车不肯说，那你们有多少枪支弹药？","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"39e952fcb3","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：具体数目不知道。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ebaacf5f97","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：又不知道。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"73b656e67b","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们全部交了。我们听军区的话，武装部发了个通知，所以我们全部交了。","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3296c2c682","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：全部上交了？","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2f6185df8a","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：绝大多数。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0e9591ed1f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那你们武斗是用冷武器，不是热武器罗！","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b6f47d96b2","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：是用木棒、钢叉，……（又改口说）我们不否认有点枪。他们有雷管、炸药……。我们坚决反对武斗。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3cf0d2c56e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们又说反对武斗，又把人家赶走。你们把武器封存起来，武器上交，撤离据点，你们干不干、","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"79c12aa089","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：干。（该监督小组，攻击桂林老多。）","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9c93ca9a22","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们在南宁把4·22压下去，桂林老多当然要来支持罗！","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9317ffe644","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：是他们压我们。我们联指从来都是高姿态、高风格的。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a8960726c3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么？人少压人多？","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ca7b65859b","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：是呀！是他们人少压我们人多。","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a2cf8971d5","type":"paragraph","text":"另外一个联指（女）：在北京我们是受害的。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"feaf18bf24","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：也许你是受害的。但是你们真正的代表不出面……。（看材料）八月十九日14时，你们调动60部汽车攻打×××仓库，有没有这件事？","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"92aa6ed374","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：……（讲不出）。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"812766eeba","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：为什么不讲？（总理念材料数字）你们枪比4·22少。呵，地区不平衡，在桂林4·22多，老多抢得多。在南宁、柳州你们（联指）枪多，比4·22多，弹药有××发，占绝对优势，大大超过人家。当然压人家。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ebb6ab5401","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们得的枪，已经写了报告。","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c5ebc79d5f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们一边抢枪，一边打报告。是不是还要打一仗？（念联指抢迫击炮、手榴弹数字）你们愿意不愿意交出来？","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"824dcd68e9","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：是他们先打我们，在北京他们还打我们！","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1ff42cd1b8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你在北京可能被打，你们在南宁、柳州打人家嘛！你要消消气，要顾全集体，要大公无私，你们能先公后私就了不起了！","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b701be8e83","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：听总理的话。","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a6fd23c290","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我的话你都讲拥护。但你们事事都说人家挑起的。你们真愿意这样做，还是对付我的？","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2fd2439864","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们在北京是受害者，我们主动……我们没有人身安全……","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0e334af51e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我不是说了吗，可能在北京你们被他们打，在南宁、柳州你们打他们罗！","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e7dd154ae8","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：总理说的话，我们坚决拥护……这是刚来的电话，八点零五分南宁开来的9025次列车，在柳州538工地，被他们大约30人抢了。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"67f808e05b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么武器？","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7202ee0d10","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：是军用的，军用物资……","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7ba54ea505","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（不耐烦地）不要说那些事了，把武器封存起来上交，允许人家回去……。","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"6d9caf576d","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：同意！","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c8d31d2079","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：同意就别说话了。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5546060219","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们在北京挑起武斗！","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f07b725bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你每一件事都说人家挑起，你们根本就没有诚意达成协议！","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0991ad9dc1","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们在北京打人，来了很多人……。","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5428a02def","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们人来的多，因为他们受压制嘛！","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bce8b1a357","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（又攻击4·22）","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"17bf152a8e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你怎么知道？什么都是他们挑起的，你既然承认广西是越南后方，个人受点委屈，又算得什么？多少战士，空军，后勤部队，就是红卫兵，也有牺牲在越南的嘛。想到他们，个人算什么！我这样开导，你们还不听嘛！？我问你，你愿意打美帝吗？","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fb2607b5d3","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：愿意。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c248235100","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：好。你到越南去，马上报名。你打下一架飞机，你的精神状态就不同了，应该恨敌人嘛，何必打自己人呢，应该往前看。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8f843788b0","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（对总理要他去越南，犹豫不答。其他联指焦急为她打气。这个女联指才回答）愿意！","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a9f25678c1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是真的，还是对付我的？","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"401ff1eda7","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：……但是，他们总是……","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0525cdafe1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：总是双方的，不是单方挑起的，两个巴掌打才响（比手势）。行了，我听听4·22的同志说了。你们4·22在南宁占领的地方是哪些？","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"540bb148ec","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：展览馆、广西日报、造反楼……。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0fa3d631f8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们人数比较少罗，不过你们还占这么多单位……","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"07f043abe4","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：我们的人都被他们赶出来，回不了工厂。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5c9d50df5c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（生气地）你们（联指）把人家从工厂里赶出来……。（又问4·22）工人被赶出去的有多少？","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"51dc417207","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：一百六十五个被赶出去，被赶出去在外地有一千多人，……在本地有些跑到指挥部，有些在其他地方，无法统计。","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e5b72511df","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：学校你们是占优势吗？","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e3a440e858","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：西大、医学院我们占优势。红卫兵总数加起来，我们也占优势。","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f27f5632a6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们要把广西局势稳定下来……。","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2103af2a7d","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：西大他们实行兵营，把我们赶出去。","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"aab7654bb0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们被赶出来，他们现在欢迎你们回去；他们被赶出去的，你们（联指）欢迎他们回来吗？过去军区支左支错了，他们要承认。现在军区决定支持你们（4·22）。第一步停止武斗。做到了，第二步就封存武器，维持革命秩序。你们拿广西大学做个试点，欢迎他们（联指）回校。观点不同，可以辩论嘛。你们（4·22）站在毛主席革命路线方面，要欢迎他们回来，慢慢地走向大联合。在这方面，你们要做个模范。（总理转过头来对南宁列车段的联指说）你们要欢迎4·22的人回去，不要吵架，不要扣工资，保证他们生活、工作。","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3cc0ee9dfe","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：愿意。","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"13a3cd78fd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不是愿意，而要欢迎。（接着总理又要橡胶厂、市委联指保证工人、机关干部能够回去，欢迎4·22的同志回去。又要郊区农民联指保证不再调农民进城搞武斗。）","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"20d7738e33","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们没有调。","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"42a25c4bb1","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：这个你不要说了。","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"149727139e","type":"paragraph","text":"（4·22递上农民进城吃去粮油数字、发票等材料）","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"44cc1162f9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理；农民以后不要进城了，要好好搞生产。","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7fe10283d0","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们现在农民没法搞生产，因为4·22挑起武斗，很多农民都跑来了。","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"91bf7abb38","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：以后谁都不准调农民进城。","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"646d24ef59","type":"paragraph","text":"（联指的那个教师又趁机要站起来发言）","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"373739e4c5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你这个教师，就是有点别扭，就是准备吵架的，就是不想达成协议。","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"84f15bf500","type":"paragraph","text":"联指（女）：（生气站起来）……","index":156,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8999f78aff","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你这样还能到前线？好，现在讲讲柳州，柳州也是个大战场。","index":157,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bc52309770","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：总理，我们“工总”被军区砸了，打成反革命！“工总”宣传委员熊一军被关在牢里，已经有四个月零三天了；还有个丁有义。我们要求平反。","index":158,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"82d7997e7d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这个事军区承认了的，下面我们还要讲。“工总”要恢复，熊一军、丁有义马上释放。（然后问柳州造反大军）你们柳州有多少人？","index":159,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9772732db6","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：有七万多人。","index":160,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a907801840","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们受压制是少数，那有七万多？","index":161,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a99fb3b897","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：以前有七万多，现在只剩下六、七千人了。","index":162,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fdbf1e9625","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这差不多。铁路是你们占优势吗？","index":163,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3c588835c8","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（向总理汇报铁路造反派受迫害情况）","index":164,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2906e54613","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们工交兵团为什么到铁路去？","index":165,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d0f0fa0532","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对总理说）是他们（联指）围他们（4·22），围得很紧。（总理叫人把柳州那两个（联指）人叫来。）","index":166,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"88a7d0845f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（柳铁4·22）原占多数，能畅通，由于他们（联指）调外单位来，搞乱了。","index":167,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2769cc8356","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（汇报各个工厂的造反派被赶出来及火车司机被抓的情况）","index":168,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1ad6c9795f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：铁路军营支持错了，你们那个地方（柳州）过去军队支左错了，破坏了正常秩序。军区要改变支左态度。","index":169,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9bab3777b8","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：支左对了，就能维持正常秩序。","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2db1b6b2e9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对，我同意你的分析。","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"26f556cd50","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（汇报全州联指架机关枪破坏铁路运输。）","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1a6a611d87","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：铁路两派观点可以保留，但不许打。你们打内战成什么样子，比军阀还厉害。以后不能动员人去干扰铁路，破坏铁路，这是命令！","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"db2449e113","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：我们知道他们（联指）破坏铁路，车不通，一夜睡不好觉。","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7d30ede5dd","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（不承认破坏铁路，说）没有。","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f17df38116","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么没有？！我都晓得有！你不在南宁，怎么晓得？你这种态度是吵架的。人家一说话，你就说是造谣，是阴谋。","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7a105ec992","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：破坏铁路涉及到军分区，武装部。他们还搞了五县联盟。（送上五县联盟材料）","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f7fb46f17a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：野战军军管的铁路，谁都不许去干扰，不要搞串连。刚才“老多”同志说，听了铁路不通车一夜睡不好觉，这种精神是好的。","index":178,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"852d160941","type":"paragraph","text":"联指（女）：（听了总理表扬老多，很生气站起来）……。","index":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"068b65e148","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你不要生气罗，你要把气愤对付美帝国主义。","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"21532636b8","type":"paragraph","text":"联指（女）：我考虑考虑。","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9cd0f85585","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：考虑！！就是对付我！你也学会了外交辞令，一、二十岁就学会了外交辞令。越南人民对你们很有感情，有的话音还相近。","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c9c8eb8b12","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：打敌人光荣，打自己人可耻。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0a223a23e4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：联指要好好想一想，你们在南宁、在柳州占优势，你们不要压4·22。你们（联指）有些保守，偏保，矛头向下，就是错的嘛！","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"0b0d135182","type":"paragraph","text":"（把头转过来对4·22说）军区压制了你们，把“工总”解散是错的。要说服联指。联指过去压迫你们不对嘛！你们在京西宾馆把韦国清同志打了一顿，这不好嘛！韦国清有错误，支左支错了，过去说过错话，压制了你们。特别是在桂林派军队镇压桂林老多。韦国清有错误。批判嘛，不要打嘛！","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ec1aa5abb5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：打韦国清是不对的，过火了点。","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4ddcd33255","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：韦国清也不因为你们这样打而改变态度。伍晋南同志，你说他们这样打对不对？","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"acfd475442","type":"paragraph","text":"伍晋南：打人是不妥当的。不对的。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"80619b8e4b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们看，你们是支持伍晋南同志的，伍晋南也说不对。领导同志是比较注意的嘛。你们青年人，火气大一些，气愤起来，一下子打了两下罗！（笑）","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1296c8e62c","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（诉苦）","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b06cc71b18","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（念十条协议）十条协议，我首先送给伟大领袖看，他看了很高兴，说这很好嘛！……现在南宁搞得最凶，其次是柳州，联指责任要大一些。在南宁、柳州对4·22你们压得多，他们不得不抵抗，4·22不得不抢枪。现在先由解放军隔开，把武器封存起来，然后拆工事，否则，铁路不通，你们一个也回不去。","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"98996c29c3","type":"paragraph","text":"（此时，被叫来的联指旁听代表进场）","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4961e716e1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对柳州工交兵团）你们为什么到铁路去。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bad3e86c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"柳指：铁路有个车辆厂参加我们兵团。","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5344dcaf5c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：铁路的要归还铁路管，你们不要去管了，铁路的要成为独立系统。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fc33c6ec79","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们要把车辆厂的少数工人（4·22）赶出去，这不行。……他们（4·22）机务段人多，他们是小包围，你们（联指）是大包围（比手势）。","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b2116d4010","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：这个问题出在军区。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bc5e2014a0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我同意你的分析，军区态度要改。","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3a172e96d4","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（汇报南宁几个被围据点没有粮食吃了）","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8223f8a806","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：由军区送去，明天给你们送去。你们不要去抢了。","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c4fb9e6c15","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（汇报首都医疗队被抓情况）","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3b4370409d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：医疗队是我派去的，怎么也抓了？！","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8e40dc07e5","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们放了，送往军区招待所，军区可以作证。","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f1fb9f70c7","type":"paragraph","text":"徐其海：（广西军区副司令员）没有！没有！联指把军区的人和医疗队都弄到东方红医院了，现在还押着。","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f52d5d7f1e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你看，军区也说了嘛，你们（联指）就是不老实。你们犯了错误，失去人心。你们的行为，把军区的两位同志（王希永、徐其海）教育清醒了。","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e422a658e5","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：你听我讲。","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"54a0c1fc01","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我听你讲什么？","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c679a1290b","type":"paragraph","text":"联指；首都医疗队支持4·22，拉一派打一派，不上我们那里去。","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e17dd9cc80","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你的态度不对嘛，我不听你啦！你们的伤员有军区医院帮你们医。他们伤的人很多，没有办法，只靠我们派去的医疗队，你们又把医疗队抓了。军区支持你们（联指）就错了嘛！","index":209,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b9d3adeb0d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：医疗队在北京是一张白纸，不带观点下去，去到那里同情他们（4·22），为什么不同情你们（联指），这说明什么问题？你们好好想一想。你们太不得人心了。","index":210,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"efa726e09f","type":"paragraph","text":"（联指诬蔑4·22活埋他们的人，要医疗队去看）","index":211,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"3d4bf41ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：人家一问，你说医疗队送回去了，又说在军区，军区说没有，你们又要医疗队看（死人）展览。看展览关他们什么事。","index":212,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b331b90230","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：王希永态度比较好。（稍停）你们（联指）打电话回去，马上把医疗队放出来，送回军区去，军区要保证他们的安全和工作便利。","index":213,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"fb4a4307d0","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22（汇报联指还抓了首都红代会和武汉三钢三新战士）","index":214,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a7f454b4ab","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：谁叫他们去的？武汉自己的问题还没有搞好，他们去不对。抓也不对，劝他们回来。","index":215,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"63fa8fed19","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（看条子）你们（联指）又把新华分社的车辆抢走了，不和新华社合作，太霸道了，这样太不得人心。（停顿）总之，医疗队、新华社、外地学生，（联指）不要抓。（4·22的）粮食由军区给你们送。中心问题是要好好与解放军合作，军区过去拉一派，打一派，是不对的。你们4·22造反派是不错的，很有劲，矛头向上，精神不错。但你们把韦国清从京西宾馆拉出来打，过火了一点。现在，军区转过来支持你们了，你们不要反过来去压人家。你们要帮助他们（联指）回到毛主席革命路线上来，共同合作，前途还是走在一起。对贺、霍你们也有错误。","index":216,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"65e77ce774","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：上当。……","index":217,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"cbb079526d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军区检查了错误，还要做军分区、人民武装部工作。梧州、百色、桂平等地问题也很严重。矛头要对准党内走资派，不要提军内一小撮，矛头不要引偏了，不要把矛头指向人民解放军。广西军区认识错误就改，这就好。","index":218,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8c2574b213","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：如果你们反过来压他们（联指），就会走向反面。","index":219,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7bb1691a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：总理，那我们的大方向不是错了吗？我是独立兵团的。我们过去也是批判反动路线的，我们也批判韦国清。我们支持韦国清是在红旗第四期社论之后，……。","index":220,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"da8b84a324","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：在某些点上你们是对的。打倒贺、霍是对的，但你们压人家就不对了！你们不要以为保韦（国清）就对了，没有什么保不保的，我们要保卫党中央，保卫毛主席！","index":221,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"03332641cc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：支持韦国清是可以的，但不能用这个口号来压对方（做手势）。","index":222,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"711233bcf9","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我们没有压。","index":223,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d245e7d95b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：事实就是压了嘛！","index":224,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"98c5e55967","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（汇报柳江旅社、贮木场、柳一中武斗事件及调动农民进城武斗的情况，要求柳联指还回尸体，请中央严肃处理）","index":225,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f0e9353c94","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：（一口否认，说一中没有打死人）","index":226,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"053f3461e8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你们一个都没有打死？","index":227,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7fac202111","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：没有。","index":228,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a37fb67689","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你说什么？一中是谁去包围的？","index":229,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"16e544511f","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：我不知道。","index":230,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1e5cf77046","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（连续问）你们去了没有？！你们去了没有？！","index":231,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"4e2b173055","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：去了。","index":232,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d2fda7056b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你是一中的吗？！","index":233,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b21e7684e9","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：不是。","index":234,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a002c311e0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你们不是一中的去干什么（连续问）？！……","index":235,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"930763c738","type":"paragraph","text":"（柳联指答不上）","index":236,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"bc2ae65f03","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：柳州军分区谁来了？知道吗？","index":237,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"595677218e","type":"paragraph","text":"黄宪（柳州军分区司令员）：一中是发生武斗，一个没有死。","index":238,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b20135c52d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：一个也没有死？你敢保证？！你说没有一个死，如果死了一个你负责。","index":239,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"9cc8b2f044","type":"paragraph","text":"黄宪：（吞吞吐吐）文化大革命以来，柳州总共死了十个。","index":240,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"50c64d0fa4","type":"paragraph","text":"黄永胜（广州军区司令员）：黄宪，伤的人明天送到军分区去治疗。","index":241,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"cf261079e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（4·22递上联指“八·一八”攻击谢副总理和王力同志的大字报照片和联指对我代表的恐吓信。）","index":242,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2b915be105","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对联指）反对谢副总理、王力同志的大字报，是你们的吧？","index":243,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e44b5a3025","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：（抵赖）不是我们的。","index":244,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"debff7dad3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：“八·一八”是你们的吗？","index":245,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"439ffd9b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"柳联：“八·一八”是我们的。","index":246,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"86079d1e69","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（手持联指恐吓信）信是你写的吧！","index":247,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"b831b50031","type":"paragraph","text":"柳指（工交兵团）：是我写的。","index":248,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5449b8bf81","type":"paragraph","text":"（4·22送上柳州联指打回柳州要屠杀造反派的电报底稿）","index":249,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"27ce2855af","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（念电报稿）这个是你打的吗？","index":250,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"8f12e07067","type":"paragraph","text":"柳指：（十分惊慌）不，不，不是我打的。","index":251,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"14e7aa3134","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：查出要严肃处理。","index":252,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"45b16863d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（4·22揭露联指盗用总理名义给他们所谓命名为“联指”。并递上他们的造谣小报。）","index":253,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a8fd78149d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我什么时候给他们命名？！","index":254,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"178ca96528","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：（揭露公、检、法干坏事，公安厅成立515武斗队）","index":255,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"cd34a3296f","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：没有！","index":256,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"2f629f964b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是公安的？","index":257,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ff0753a75f","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：我是西大的。","index":258,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"d4e752b89b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：为什么替公安辩护？","index":259,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"febf3aa229","type":"paragraph","text":"（联指不敢回答）","index":260,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"6a52a28be3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对公、检、法要一分为二。公、检、法过去受彭真、罗瑞卿控制，有很多思想和作风是反毛泽东思想的。搞跟踪、搞盯梢、偷听电话、搞特务活动，甚至挑动是非。公、检、法一定要搞大的斗批改，才能彻底肃清罗瑞卿的流毒。……。两个月没有接见你们了，一定有很多事要讲。现在你们双方停止武斗，然后把枪封存，地方和铁路分开，不要破坏交通，要保障铁路畅通，任何一派都不准冲击铁路。今后任何人都不得调动农民进城。要欢迎对方回到本单位，西大做个模范。","index":261,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"38d56d31ac","type":"paragraph","text":"联指（女）：（受了批评，哭了）总理，那我们是什么组织？","index":262,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5a4e3f97c4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么组织？群众组织嘛，要革命的话，就是革命组织。","index":263,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"07308bfa54","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们要宰了我。","index":264,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"979ad489cc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不会，不会，那里会！","index":265,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"030d9ec1c4","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：（暴跳如雷）……","index":266,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"f9dca1b470","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你这个人叫什么？呵，任树人（小8代表），最爱吵架。","index":267,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"a315ece4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"联指：他们叫我们联匪，我们也要求平反。","index":268,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"e26b10caf7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们（4·22）以后不要叫他们联匪了。","index":269,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"36d3f9f241","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：好，今后我们一定不叫了。","index":270,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7e17039675","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：好好好，他们答应不叫了嘛！（笑）","index":271,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"ba89547995","type":"paragraph","text":"4·22：要求广西军区把致“新工总”、“倒海翻江”忠告、警告书撤销、平反。","index":272,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"36bb65f138","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：已经讲了，军区要承认错误，平反嘛！","index":273,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"7f0d47a57f","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时女联指还在哭）","index":274,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"81d001e388","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们广西人很坚强，韦国清打仗很勇猛，是一个猛将么。这个月一定解决你们广西问题。桂林搞得不错嘛，可着手商量“三结合”革命委员会。你们“老多”做得不坏，在广西是造反派带头的一批，要做两边的工作。","index":275,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"c29623bbca","type":"paragraph","text":"（“老多”表示一定做联指工作，欢迎他们回到毛主席的革命路线上来。）","index":276,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"1daf6aa227","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理、戚本禹同志挥动语录本与代表告别）","index":277,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"},{"id":"5c587b12e7","type":"paragraph","text":"（高呼毛主席万岁！）","index":278,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b"}],"page":{"id":"c57d5c905f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b314fc3b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}